Titolo: Hot Chase

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Hot Chase is an arcade game released in 1988 by Konami.  In the game, players drive a white Porsche 959 out of an enemy country to the Border crossing of a friendly one.  The car has a bomb attached to it that explodes in a set time. If the bomb explodes, players must restart. There are many obstacles along the way, including railroad crossings, military checkpoints, helicopters that shoot at the car and other cars. The gameplay is said to be similar to Chase H.Q..

Genere: Driving 

Valutazione: 80
